bscr - screenshot utility
=========================
bscr is a simple screenshot utility for x.

Requirements
------------
bscr requires libpng, libxcb and its extensions, libxkbcommon, and xclip.

Installation
------------
bscr comes with a Makefile and config.mk file for configurable building and
testing.  Edit the latter to match your local setup (bscr is installed into the
/usr/local namespace by default, you may need to modify your $PATH).

bscr can be built and installed with the following command (run as root):

    make clean install

